---
title: "El Blog de Carlos"
layout: "layouts/base.njk"
---

<style>
    .post-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .card {
        transform-style: preserve-3d;
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
        transform: translateZ(20px) rotateX(5deg) rotateY(-5deg);
    }
    .card-content {
        transition: background-color 0.4s ease;
    }
    .card:hover .card-content {
        background-color: #1f2937; /* bg-gray-800 */
    }
    .card-image-wrapper {
        filter: grayscale(100%);
        transition: filter 0.4s ease;
    }
    .card:hover .card-image-wrapper {
        filter: grayscale(0%);
    }
    .card-title {
        transition: color 0.4s ease;
    }
    .card:hover .card-title {
        color: #f59e0b; /* text-amber-500 */
    }
    .hero-char {
        display: inline-block;
    }
</style>
<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center text-center">
    <div class="px-6">
        <h1 class="hero-title text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-gray-200">
            <span class="hero-char">I</span>
            <span class="hero-char">A</span>
            <span class="hero-char"></span>
            <span class="hero-char"></span>
            <span class="hero-char">B</span>
            <span class="hero-char">L</span>
            <span class="hero-char">O</span>
            <span class="hero-char">G</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="hero-subtitle text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
            <p>
                Un espacio para la exploración tecnológica, el diseño interactivo y la creatividad digital en la era de la inteligencia
                artificial.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-500">
                Aquí encontrarás análisis, tutoriales y una visión crítica sobre las herramientas y tendencias que están definiendo
                nuestro futuro.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- POSTS GRID -->
<main class="px-6 md:px-12 pb-20 -mt-16">
    {% set posts = collections.post | reverse %}
    <div class="post-grid max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        {% for post in posts %}
            {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
                <article class="card h-full">
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block h-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700/50">
                        <div class="card-content flex flex-col h-full">
                            <div class="card-image-wrapper aspect-video overflow-hidden">
                                <img src="{{ post.data.image or 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d1469c9b?q=80&w=870&auto=format&fit=crop' }}" alt="Imagen para {{ post.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-400 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-105 aspect-ratio-16/9"></div>
                                <div class="p-8 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                                    <h2 class="card-title text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-3 flex-grow">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
                                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-3">{{ post.data.description or "Explora este artículo para descubrir insights, código y nuevas perspectivas." }}</p>
                                    {% if post.data.date %}
                                        <p class="text-xs text-amber-500 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">
                                            <time datetime="{{ post.date | date('iso') }}">{{ post.date | date }}</time>
                                        </p>
                                    {% endif %}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </article>
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-16">
            <a
                href="/archive"
                class="more-posts-btn inline-flex items-center text-amber-500 font-semibold text-lg hover:text-amber-400
                    transition-colors">
                Ver todos los artículos
                <div class="ml-2">→</div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>